@NewPinpadApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5125

### Test Database Status
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/DatabaseStatus
Accept: application/json

### Seed Sample Data (run this first to populate database)
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/SeedSampleData
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Regionals
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/GetRegionals
Accept: application/json

### Get All Branches
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/GetBranches
Accept: application/json

### Get Active Branches Only
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/GetBranches?status=active
Accept: application/json

### Get All Pinpads
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/GetPinpads
Accept: application/json

### Get Active Pinpads Only
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/GetPinpads?status=active
Accept: application/json

### Add New Regional
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/AddRegional
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Code": "REG002",
  "Name": "Regional Surabaya"
}

### Add New Branch
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/AddBranch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "RegionalId": 1,
  "Class": "active",
  "Code": "B003",
  "Name": "Cabang Surabaya",
  "IpLow": "192.168.3.1",
  "IpHigh": "192.168.3.10"
}

### Add New Pinpad
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/AddPinpad
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "PpadSn": "SN003",
  "PpadBranch": 3,
  "PpadBranchLama": 0,
  "PpadStatus": "Active",
  "PpadStatusRepair": "None",
  "PpadStatusLama": "Inactive",
  "PpadTid": "TID003",
  "PpadFlag": 1
}

### Export Pinpad Data - GET Method (akan ada delay 2 detik)
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export?format=csv
Accept: application/json

### Export Pinpad Data with Filters - GET Method
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export?format=xlsx&status=Active&branch=1
Accept: application/json

### Export Pinpad Data by Serial Number - GET Method
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export?format=pdf&serialNumber=SN001
Accept: application/json

### Export Pinpad Data - POST Method (lebih fleksibel)
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Format": "csv",
  "Status": "Active",
  "Branch": "1",
  "SerialNumber": "SN001"
}

### Export Pinpad Data to Excel - POST Method
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Format": "xlsx",
  "Status": "Active"
}

### Export Pinpad Data to PDF - POST Method
POST {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/api/Pinpad/pinpads/export
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Format": "pdf",
  "Branch": "2"
}

### Weather Forecast (existing endpoint)
GET {{NewPinpadApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json
